{
  "title": "V1: Anti-Pattern — Counter-based Pushgateway (Broken)",
  "uid": "airflow-v1-anti-pattern",
  "tags": ["airflow", "v1", "anti-pattern", "lab"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "dag_id",
        "label": "DAG",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(task_status_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\"}, dag_id)",
        "sort": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true
      },
      {
        "name": "task_id",
        "label": "Task",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(task_status_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"}, task_id)",
        "sort": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## ❌ V1: Anti-Pattern Dashboard\nThis plugin uses Prometheus **Counters** without `run_id` in the grouping key.\n\n**Anti-Pattern 1 — Race Condition:** When multiple tasks run in parallel, they all write to the same Pushgateway slot. The last push wins — earlier pushes are silently overwritten.\n\n**Anti-Pattern 2 — Counter Semantics:** If a task fails then retries and succeeds, `task_status_total{state=\"failed\"}` is never erased. Both failure and success are permanently counted.\n\nEnable with: `AIRFLOW_VAR_ENABLE_V1_COUNTERS=true`"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Successes Recorded (Counter — will undercount under parallel load)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(task_status_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", task_id=~\"$task_id\", state=\"success\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Successes",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Failures Recorded (Counter — will undercount under parallel load)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(task_status_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", task_id=~\"$task_id\", state=\"failed\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Failures",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 }] }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "task_status_total Over Time — Counter Accumulation",
      "description": "Notice how concurrent task pushes collapse into a single value due to the missing run_id. The counter does not represent all events.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 10, "w": 24, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "task_status_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", task_id=~\"$task_id\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{dag_id}} / {{task_id}} — {{state}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } }
    }
  ]
}
